author: @ThassioMarcelo
content: I was there, it was magical! Brazil is the best place on earth, or like Madonna said: PARADISE. nowhere in this world this would happen. While countries does wars for power, we celebrate life with joy. the COME TO BRAZIL quote is like a invitation from angels to heaven! don't miss your calling!
